headline: H2O.ai Unveils 2025 AI 100 Award Winners: Celebrating Global Leaders Building the Future of AI
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., October 22, 2025--H2O.ai, the world’s leading agentic AI company and a pioneer in sovereign AI, today announced the winners of the 2025 H2O AI 100, an annual list recognizing innovators, operators, and researchers advancing the real-world impact of artificial intelligence across industries and borders.

headline: Piper Sandler: Dell a beneficiary of the upcoming datacenter refresh
summary: Investing.com -- Piper Sandler analysts initiated coverage on Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL) with an Overweight rating and a $172 price target, while starting Hewlett Packard Enterprise (NYSE: HPE) at Neutral with a $24 target, citing contrasting strengths and execution risks between the two enterprise hardware players.
